  "detailed_description": "Features a day and night cycle, various survival mechanics, controls somewhat like top down MOBA / ARPG with freely turn-able camera.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLearn unique class based abilities, grow more powerful through skill trees, level up your anima and equipment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCraft various items, consumables, and defend yourself from bosses and hostile monsters at night.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaying the tutorial at least once is recommended!",
